  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6e96e5e50fc682e1726f60b0c873485e.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6e96e5e50fc682e1726f60b0c873485e.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6e96e5e50fc682e1726f60b0c873485e.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rev up your engines, it’s almost time to race back to the past with Rally Arcade Classics! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you are a veteran craving for some good old arcade rally game, or a rookie that is willing to take the challenge and race versus racing legends, Rally Arcade Classics puts on the table every ingredient to experience a rush to the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/379c30912047ea15f7c126f295763d8c.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/379c30912047ea15f7c126f295763d8c.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/379c30912047ea15f7c126f295763d8c.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Including 44 iconic cars from the 70’s, 80’s, 90’s and 00’s, and 48 thrilling tracks to rev up their engines to the max while drifting every close turn, you will never run out of challenges to take upon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed is (almost) everything. Beat every timer, collect credits to purchase faster cars, collect golden cups and stars to unlock more challenges in the following game modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/37778c6a445cc9eb0946e56bc6aa73f3.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/37778c6a445cc9eb0946e56bc6aa73f3.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/37778c6a445cc9eb0946e56bc6aa73f3.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Licences</strong>: Before you take the wheel behind one of the legendary rally cars, you got to test yourself and get the licence to drive them in 10 custom made tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/0d4e6065b19767e63b3a105417078017.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/0d4e6065b19767e63b3a105417078017.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/0d4e6065b19767e63b3a105417078017.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tour:</strong> Race through a variety of challenges across four different countries to get credits, stars and the reigning spot of nº1 on the online leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/5dce4c2d4d7a9db0dc5a9b9146411e3a.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/5dce4c2d4d7a9db0dc5a9b9146411e3a.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/5dce4c2d4d7a9db0dc5a9b9146411e3a.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade:</strong> Get your hand full with 16 unique old arcade challenges, where you will race against 14 other drivers across 4 different tracks to reign supreme as the winner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6cb502396374f533c0e48a9c62125d74.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6cb502396374f533c0e48a9c62125d74.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6cb502396374f533c0e48a9c62125d74.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rally:</strong> The classic mode, where you will drive through one of the four countries rallies, racing neck to neck with legendary drivers to conquer the gold cup. With 3 different difficulty levels, and 3 different wheel drives car categories, we exchange exhausting hour-long gameplays for some quick and always-changing short bursts of action with much more variety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/8374dff4d19de12c56517fd4bc67e6c4.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/8374dff4d19de12c56517fd4bc67e6c4.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/8374dff4d19de12c56517fd4bc67e6c4.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Events:</strong> Weekly and monthly events, where everyone gets the same track, car and weather conditions and climb to the top score on the leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/287340fe273ea7fc2e2687df813cadcc.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/287340fe273ea7fc2e2687df813cadcc.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/287340fe273ea7fc2e2687df813cadcc.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chrono:</strong> You can choose country, track, car, time of the day and weather conditions to test yourself on different cars and road conditions to amp up your game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rev up your engines, it’s almost time to race back to the past!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6e96e5e50fc682e1726f60b0c873485e.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6e96e5e50fc682e1726f60b0c873485e.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6e96e5e50fc682e1726f60b0c873485e.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rev up your engines, it’s almost time to race back to the past with Rally Arcade Classics! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you are a veteran craving for some good old arcade rally game, or a rookie that is willing to take the challenge and race versus racing legends, Rally Arcade Classics puts on the table every ingredient to experience a rush to the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/379c30912047ea15f7c126f295763d8c.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/379c30912047ea15f7c126f295763d8c.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/379c30912047ea15f7c126f295763d8c.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Including 44 iconic cars from the 70’s, 80’s, 90’s and 00’s, and 48 thrilling tracks to rev up their engines to the max while drifting every close turn, you will never run out of challenges to take upon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed is (almost) everything. Beat every timer, collect credits to purchase faster cars, collect golden cups and stars to unlock more challenges in the following game modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/37778c6a445cc9eb0946e56bc6aa73f3.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/37778c6a445cc9eb0946e56bc6aa73f3.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/37778c6a445cc9eb0946e56bc6aa73f3.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Licences</strong>: Before you take the wheel behind one of the legendary rally cars, you got to test yourself and get the licence to drive them in 10 custom made tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/0d4e6065b19767e63b3a105417078017.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/0d4e6065b19767e63b3a105417078017.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/0d4e6065b19767e63b3a105417078017.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tour:</strong> Race through a variety of challenges across four different countries to get credits, stars and the reigning spot of nº1 on the online leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/5dce4c2d4d7a9db0dc5a9b9146411e3a.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/5dce4c2d4d7a9db0dc5a9b9146411e3a.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/5dce4c2d4d7a9db0dc5a9b9146411e3a.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade:</strong> Get your hand full with 16 unique old arcade challenges, where you will race against 14 other drivers across 4 different tracks to reign supreme as the winner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6cb502396374f533c0e48a9c62125d74.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6cb502396374f533c0e48a9c62125d74.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/6cb502396374f533c0e48a9c62125d74.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rally:</strong> The classic mode, where you will drive through one of the four countries rallies, racing neck to neck with legendary drivers to conquer the gold cup. With 3 different difficulty levels, and 3 different wheel drives car categories, we exchange exhausting hour-long gameplays for some quick and always-changing short bursts of action with much more variety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/8374dff4d19de12c56517fd4bc67e6c4.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/8374dff4d19de12c56517fd4bc67e6c4.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/8374dff4d19de12c56517fd4bc67e6c4.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Events:</strong> Weekly and monthly events, where everyone gets the same track, car and weather conditions and climb to the top score on the leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/287340fe273ea7fc2e2687df813cadcc.poster.avif?t=1755289544\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/287340fe273ea7fc2e2687df813cadcc.webm?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837580/extras/287340fe273ea7fc2e2687df813cadcc.mp4?t=1755289544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chrono:</strong> You can choose country, track, car, time of the day and weather conditions to test yourself on different cars and road conditions to amp up your game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rev up your engines, it’s almost time to race back to the past!</p>",
